het Jonas. And he left them, and departed.","year":32},{"id":"rec83MJgftWGpVxo8","ref":"Matt.16.5","text":"And when his disciples were come to the other side, they had forgotten to take bread.","year":32},{"id":"recasOIn8gOMNeUa7","ref":"Matt.16.6","text":"Then Jesus said unto them, Take heed and beware of the leaven of the Pharisees and of the Sadducees.","year":32},{"id":"rectZiFiErIp6Ib8f","ref":"Matt.16.7","text":"And they reasoned among themselves, saying, It is because we have taken no bread.","year":32},{"id":"recAew2oPrxQEZR2A","ref":"Matt.16.8","text":"Which when Jesus perceived, he said unto them, O ye of little faith, why reason ye among yourselves, because ye have brought no bread?","year":32}]}
